      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i look in the mirror and i dont even recognize the person looking back. it feels like the real me—the one with dreams and actual life in them—died a long time ago. i'm just... moving through the motions now. like a ghost haunted by a person who isn't there anymore.",
